productBaseInfoV1.title: Lenovo Yoga 8 B6000 Tablet
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Blending perfection with quality to produce a device that is sure to amaze you, this Lenovo Yoga 8 B6000 Tablet gives you a versatile yet complete tablet experience. Multimode Stylish Design Built in an extremely versatile and convenient design with a sleek structure, this Lenovo Tab makes it easy for you to hold, tilt and make the Tab stand according to your usage. 8 Inch Display with Wide Viewing Angles Manufactured with a broad 8 inch display that gives you an incredible viewing experience, this Tab also extends the feature with wide viewing angles for an even more enhanced display. The device also comes with the option of connecting and sharing data and media with other devices using the OTG cable, Micro USB and Bluetooth options. Camera Built with a 5MP primary camera and 1.6 MP secondary camera, this device lets you click away special moment and also make video calls and chat as and when you please. Storage Store all your personal data, videos and music and carry them around with you in this Tab; and if you feel this 16GB storage is insufficient, you could extend the memory space up to 64GB by inserting a microSD card into the slot provided. Battery Experience an uninterrupted usage while you work, watch videos or play games, because this device is designed with an enhanced battery backup that lasts longer.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Apple iPad mini 2 32 GB 7.9 inch with Wi-Fi Only
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Portability comes to the palm with the iPad Mini with Retina Display that balances the perfect design that Apple is renowned for with a spec line-up that promises great performance. Display 7.9 inches of Retina Display brings perfect, sharp and almost life-like visuals to the eye – watching a movie, playing a game or even just browsing through a few photos will be a pleasure considering the screen has over 3.1 million pixels on the 2048 x 1536 resolution, a million more than an HDTV and 4x better than the 1st generation iPad Mini. With LED backlighting and IPS technology, the multitouch screen makes multitasking easy. It also sports oleophobic coating ensures that what your view is not covered with fingerprints and smudges, despite constant use. Processor Powered by Apple’s home-grown A7 chip with 64-bit architecture, this iPad Mini processes functions efficiently to give you good speed. Apps you open are launched at lightning speed and the graphics-rich game runs without any hitches or lag with the A7 processor. It also supports OpenGLES v3.0 that adds more detail to the graphics and visual effects. Complementing the A7 is the M7 motion coprocessor that lends efficiency to the built-in sensors to allow the apps to adapt to the functions and give you a customized, intuitive performance and responsiveness. Battery Life Working together and dividing the load between themselves, the A7 chip and the M7 motion coprocessor ensure that there is great battery management to give you up to 10 hours of battery life. Camera Armed with the 5 megapixel iSight camera, this iPad Mini lets you frame and click crisp, bright pictures with great exposure and clarity whenever you want, wherever you are. The camera works with the image signal processor in the A7 chip to adjust the details automatically, letting you click the perfect photograph without any manual effort or adjustments. What’s more, capture the entire moment to relive at another time in full 1080p HD video with just a swipe on the screen. A 1.2 megapixel front camera allows you to video chat with a loved one with good clarity and detail; conversations look and feel better on this FaceTime HD camera. The camera features a backside illumination sensor to allow for more light to be captured, amping up the overall feel and brightness of every picture you take on this secondary camera. The device also comes with built-in dual microphones that minimizes background noise and enhances audio quality. iOS 7 The iPad Mini with Retina Display runs on iOS 7 that is designed to perfectly match the capabilities of the hardware that it packs and make full use of it. An operating system that is familiar yet simpler and smarter, the iOS 7 lets you multitask in an intelligent manner and features Siri, the voice assistant that will help you perform tasks without ever touching the tablet. With a Control Centre to aid simple functioning, Notification Centre to collate alerts and the iCloud to back-up data, the iOS 7 gives you a rounded experience. Connectivity Designed to always keep you connected, this iPad Mini comes with dual-band Wi-Fi support that makes use of two antennas and MIMO technology to ensure that you have fast browsing and download speeds of up to 300 Mbps. Sharing photos via AirDrop, catching up on your favorite shows and everything else on the web is so much faster. It is also Bluetooth-enabled that lets you share data with other Apple devices. App Store The Mini comes with pre-installed apps like the iPhoto, iMovie, GarageBand, Pages, Numbers and Keynote to start you off on your quest for utilitarian entertainment. Sensors The iPad Mini comes with a three-axis gyro and an accelerometer, sensors that work together to detect motion to allow you to play games and react intuitively when you move around. The ambient light sensor aims to adjust screen lighting according to the surroundings to ensure that the screen is just the right level of brightness for your eyes to view. Storage Capacity This iPad Mini comes with 32 GB of space which allows you to store all your apps, favorite songs, pictures and videos.

productBaseInfoV1.title: SAMSUNG Galaxy Tab S2 3 GB RAM 32 GB ROM 9.7 inch with Wi-Fi+4G Tablet (White)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Experience life in HD with Samsung Galaxy S2 tablet (WiFi, 4G, voice calling) - White. Work, play, do, watch, listen and communicate with the super sleek and stylish 4G tablet from Samsung. The S2 tablet runs on 1.9GHz quad core+1.3GHz quad core Exynos processor and is based on Android v5 Lollipop OS to meet new age communication needs. Storage and memory needs are met through 3GB RAM and 32GB built-in storage space with an extendable storage option upto 128GB. The single SIM tablet comes with 9.7-inch (24.63cm) sAMOLED capacitive touchscreen for big stunning views and lets you capture life's moments with 8MP primary camera. Powered by 5870mAh battery, the voice calling tablet feels just right in your hand with 5.6mm slender form and facilitates selfie fun with 2.1MP front facing camera. Connectivity is achieved through 4G, Bluetooth 4.1 BLE, WiFi Hotspot, Wi-Fi Direct, voice calling, Video Calls, GPS and utility through Music Player, Video Player, Accelerometer, eCompass, Gyroscope, Finger scanner, Hall sensor, finger print scanner. Users can work on documents with on-board MS Office suite, gain access to OneDrive 100GB cloud storage for 2 years, run and work on two apps side by side with multi window feature and better manage the device through centralised dashboard.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Apple iPad Air 16 GB 9.7 inch with Wi-Fi+3G
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Styled to be the lightest tablet yet, the iPad Air is a powerhouse of performance packed into one sleek package, effectively highlighting the design prowess Apple is known for. Design The iPad Air features a body that can be deemed slim, sporting a height of 9.4 inches and a width of 6.6 inches. Accompanying you in your daily life and becoming an extension of your arm, the tablet will hardly weigh you down. The aluminium unibody design deserves much more than just a passing glance - while being unobtrusive, it is also durable enough to stand the rigors of everyday existence. Display With thinner bezels and overall width, the focus will be on the content itself rather than the device. The 9.7 inch Retina display of the iPad Air, with a pixel density of 264 ppi and a screen resolution of 2048 x 1536, treats your eyes to a stunning array of colors in every visual, with just the right amount of brightness and astounding clarity. With LED backlighting and IPS technology, the multitouch screen makes multitasking easy. It also sports oleophobic coating ensures that what your view is not covered with fingerprints and smudges, despite constant use. Processor Powered by Apple's home-grown A7 chip with 64-bit architecture, this iPad Air processes functions efficiently to give you good speed. Apps you open are launched at lightning speed and the graphics-rich game runs without any hitches or lag with the A7 processor. It also supports OpenGLES v3.0 that adds more detail to the graphics and visual effects. Complementing the A7 is the M7 motion coprocessor that lends efficiency to the built-in sensors to allow the apps to adapt to the functions and give you a customized, intuitive performance and responsiveness. Camera Armed with the 5 megapixel iSight camera, this iPad Air lets you frame and click crisp, bright pictures with great exposure and clarity whenever you want, wherever you are. The camera works with the image signal processor in the A7 chip to adjust the details automatically, letting you click the perfect photograph without any manual effort or adjustments. What's more, capture the entire moment to relive at another time in full 1080p HD video with just a swipe on the screen. A 1.2 megapixel front camera, aided by dual microphones, allows you to video chat with a loved one with good clarity and detail; conversations look and feel better on this FaceTime HD camera. The camera features a backside illumination sensor to allow for more light to be captured in every frame. iOS 7 The iPad Air runs on iOS 7 that is designed to perfectly match the capabilities of the hardware that it packs and make full use of it. An operating system that is familiar yet simpler and smarter, the iOS 7 lets you multitask in an intelligent manner and features Siri, the voice assistant that will help you perform tasks without ever touching the tablet. With a Control Centre to aid simple functioning, Notification Centre to collate alerts and the iCloud to back-up data, the iOS 7 gives you a rounded experience.  Connectivity Designed to always keep you connected, this iPad Air comes with dual-band Wi-Fi support that makes use of two antennas and MIMO technology to ensure that you have fast browsing and download speeds of up to 300 Mbps. Sharing photos via AirDrop, catching up on your favorite shows and everything else on the web is so much faster. With 3G support, the iPad Air can be used not only to link up to the internet but also act as a cellular hotspot for other devices as well. It is also Bluetooth-enabled to let you share data with other Apple devices. Battery Life With efficient power and task management by the processor, the iPad Air can last up to 10 hours, allowing you ample time to ensure that you have enough juice to browse, watch videos, click pretty pictures and read your favorite books without the need to find a charging point every so often. App Store The Air comes with pre-installed apps like the iPhoto, iMovie, GarageBand, Pages, Numbers and Keynote to start you off on the quest for utilitarian entertainment. Sensors A range of sensors help the iPad Air be as intuitive as it is - a three-axis gyro acts in cohesion with an accelerometer for better motion sensing that comes in handy when you play games among other things. The ambient light sensor detects the brightness around to adjust the display brightness for an optimized viewing experience and better battery management. Storage Capacity This iPad Air comes with 16 GB of space which allows you to store all your apps, favorite songs, pictures and videos.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Apple iPad mini with Retina Display 64 GB 7.9 inch with Wi-Fi+3G
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Portability comes to the palm with the iPad Mini with Retina Display that balances the perfect design that Apple is renowned for with a spec line-up that promises great performance. Display 7.9 inches of Retina Display brings perfect, sharp and almost life-like visuals to the eye - watching a movie, playing a game or even just browsing through a few photos will be a pleasure considering the screen has over 3.1 million pixels on the 2048 x 1536 resolution, a million more than an HDTV and 4x better than the 1st generation iPad Mini. With LED backlighting and IPS technology, the multitouch screen makes multitasking easy. It also sports oleophobic coating ensures that what your view is not covered with fingerprints and smudges, despite constant use. Processor Powered by Apple's home-grown A7 chip with 64-bit architecture, this iPad Mini processes functions efficiently to give you good speed. Apps you open are launched at lightning speed and the graphics-rich game runs without any hitches or lag with the A7 processor. It also supports OpenGLES v3.0 that adds more detail to the graphics and visual effects. Complementing the A7 is the M7 motion coprocessor that lends efficiency to the built-in sensors to allow the apps to adapt to the functions and give you a customized, intuitive performance and responsiveness. Battery Life Working together and dividing the load between themselves, the A7 chip and the M7 motion coprocessor ensure that there is great battery management to give you up to 10 hours of battery life. Camera Armed with the 5 megapixel iSight camera, this iPad Mini lets you frame and click crisp, bright pictures with great exposure and clarity whenever you want, wherever you are. The camera works with the image signal processor in the A7 chip to adjust the details automatically, letting you click the perfect photograph without any manual effort or adjustments. What's more, capture the entire moment to relive at another time in full 1080p HD video with just a swipe on the screen. A 1.2 megapixel front camera allows you to video chat with a loved one with good clarity and detail; conversations look and feel better on this FaceTime HD camera. The camera features a backside illumination sensor to allow for more light to be captured, amping up the overall feel and brightness of every picture you take on this secondary camera. The device also comes with built-in dual microphones that minimizes background noise and enhances audio quality. iOS 7 The iPad Mini with Retina Display runs on iOS 7 that is designed to perfectly match the capabilities of the hardware that it packs and make full use of it. An operating system that is familiar yet simpler and smarter, the iOS 7 lets you multitask in an intelligent manner and features Siri, the voice assistant that will help you perform tasks without ever touching the tablet. With a Control Centre to aid simple functioning, Notification Centre to collate alerts and the iCloud to back-up data, the iOS 7 gives you a rounded experience. Connectivity Designed to always keep you connected, this iPad Mini comes with dual-band Wi-Fi support that makes use of two antennas and MIMO technology to ensure that you have fast browsing and download speeds of up to 300 Mbps which is double the speed of the 1st generation iPad Mini. Sharing photos via AirDrop, catching up on your favorite shows and everything else on the web is so much faster. With 3G support, the iPad Mini with Retina Display can be used not only to link up to the World Wide Web but also act as a cellular hotspot for other devices as well. It is also Bluetooth-enabled to let you share data with other Apple devices. App Store The Mini comes with pre-installed apps like the iPhoto, iMovie, GarageBand, Pages, Numbers and Keynote to start you off on the quest for utilitarian entertainment. Sensors The iPad Mini comes with a three-axis gyro and an accelerometer, sensors that work together to detect motion to allow you to play games and react intuitively when you move around. The ambient light sensor aims to adjust screen lighting according to the surroundings to ensure that the screen is just the right level of bright for your eyes to view. Storage Capacity This iPad Mini comes with 64 GB of space which allows you to store all your apps, favorite songs, pictures and videos.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Smartbeats SB-N5 2 GB RAM 16 GB ROM 7 inch with Wi-Fi+4G Tablet (White)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: The Smartbeats 4G Calling Tablet is what you want to look at if you are searching for a tablet for immersive entertainment. Buy now and enjoy 4G superfast speed by Airtel Vodafone idea or latest JIO Network. Smartbeats Tablet support both LTE and VoLTE 4G network. This Tablet have latest Mirror Screen feature, WiFi hotspot Feature and many more. This tablet comes with a dual SIM option, which allows you to use either or both slots at the same time. With a 17.78 cm / 7 inch TFT HD display, it is easy to fit your tablet almost anywhere while carrying it. It also comes with a display resolution of 1024 x 600 pixels which gives you clear and vibrant images on the screen. The Smartbeats Tablet runs on the fastest Android v6.0 OS platform which is also known as Marshmallow. It has a Quad Core processor which runs with a speed of 1.3GHz. A tablet with a fast processor is mainly dependent on the RAM. The RAM is 2GB which facilitates smooth and faster functioning of the device. Learn to love taking pictures with this tablet. With its clear picture quality and good shutter speed, its 5.0MP rear camera and an LED flash make your pictures brighter. It also has a 2.0MP front camera which allows you to take great selfies to captures your precious moments. If you are looking for a tablet with good connectivity, this is the tablet for you. It supports GPS, Bluetooth, radio, 2G 3G and 4G voice calling & 4G Video Calling. The hardware connectivity that is available is the 3.5mm audio jack port. It is important to have a tablet where you can carry as much data as you need. Though the internal memory is 16GB, the external memory is expandable up to 64GB which will allow you to store your world onto your tablet. The Smartbeats Tablet is powered by 3000 mAh Polymer - ion battery type, video playback around 5 hours, and standby time approx 15 days. This Tablet is preloaded with latest apps whatsapp, facebook, Twitter, Youtube, Gmail, Skype, and exclusive100 HD quality video songs. With Mirror cast, you can connect the tablet to your TV or Projector and watch your favourite photos and videos on large screen without any wiring hassles.

productBaseInfoV1.title: Google Nexus 7 2013 Tablet
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: Work, play and entertain yourself with the latest Nexus 7 that brings a whole bunch of fun and functional features to your fingertips. Display Indulge in an incredibly awesome viewing experience with the 7-inch 1920x1200 resolution display that projects crystal clear images while you watch videos come alive with the vibrant High Definition video output. Powerhouse Packed with maximised power to deliver a smooth and dynamic performance, this Nexus Tab is built with a 1.5GHz Qualcomm Snapdragon S4 Processor with a 2 GB of RAM that ensures a fast and high performance especially while running multiple apps and playing games. OS Powered by the Android v4.3 Jelly Bean operating system, this device offers a fun, easy and fast user interface that lets you customise a whole lot of features making it feel more of your own while ensuring excellent fluidity while in use. Camera Built with a 5MP primary camera and 1.2MP secondary camera, the Nexus 7 lets you capture special moments while also letting you video chat with your loved ones bridging distance. Make use of the Full HD video recording to capture videos at its best quality. Storage The device offers 16GB of data storage space that you can lavishly use to store all your favourite music, videos and more while also capturing photos and videos without having to worry about the storage space. Connectivity Connect to the internet with absolutely no hassle using the built-in Wi-Fi feature and explore the World Wide Web to the fullest. The USB and Bluetooth connectivity feature of this Tab lets you connect to other devices that support the same to transfer data and media with ease. Battery Life Kill your boredom playing games or surfing the net while you’re at home or travelling, because this device ensures a longer lasting battery power that keeps the device alive for longer than you expected. Sensors This Nexus is built with an Ambient Light Sensor to make the display more convenient while the other sensors include the Gyroscope, e-Compass and G-Sensor that gives you a better user experience.

productBaseInfoV1.title: I Kall 4GN5 2 GB RAM 16 GB ROM 7 inch with Wi-Fi+4G Tablet (Black)
productBaseInfoV1.productDescription: The I Kall 4G Calling Tablet is what you want to look at if you are searching for a tablet for immersive entertainment. Buy now and enjoy 4G superfast speed. I Kall Tablet support both LTE and VoLTE 4G network. This tablet comes with a dual SIM option, which allows you to use either or both slots at the same time. With a 17.78 cm TFT HD display, it is easy to fit your tablet almost anywhere while carrying it. It also comes with a display resolution of 1024 x 600 pixels which gives you clear and vibrant images on the screen. The I Kall Tablet runs on the latest and fastest Android v6.0 OS platform which is also known as Marshmallow. It has a Quad Core MTK processor which runs with a speed of 1.3GHz. A tablet with a fast processor is mainly dependent on the RAM. The RAM is 2GB which facilitates smooth and faster functioning of the device. Learn to love taking pictures with this tablet. With its clear picture quality and good shutter speed, its 5.0MP rear camera and an LED flash make your pictures brighter. It also has a 2.0MP front camera which allows you to take great selfies to captures your precious moments. If you are looking for a tablet with good connectivity, this is the tablet for you. It supports GPS, Bluetooth, radio, 2G and 3G voice calling. The hardware connectivity that is available is the 3.5mm audio jack port. It is important to have a tablet where you can carry as much data as you need. Though the internal memory is 16GB, the external memory is expandable up to 32GB which will allow you to store your world onto your tablet. The I Kall Tablet is powered by 3000 mAh lithium - ion battery type.

It is important to have a tablet where you can carry as much data as you need. Though the internal memory is 16GB, the external memory is expandable up to 32GB which will allow you to store your world onto your tablet.
